K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-1: dge bsnyen ma dang 'jig rten pa rnams kyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-2: nga yi rigs kyi gsang sngags bzlas brjod na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-3: de dag rnams kyis lus ni myur du 'jig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-4: gang zhig nga rigs rjes su 'brang ba'i gdon //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-7: gang zhig theg mchog rgya chen klog pa dang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-11: ngas ni 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas pa'i //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-13: de nas gzhan yang 'jig rten pa bsdus nas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-14: zhar la bshad pa 'di dag khyod kyis nyon //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-20: me yis kyang ni brgya phrag bdun nyid dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-21: phur bu gsum pa yis ni stong bshad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171a-22: klu mi rgyal po rnams kyis lnga stong ste //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-0: mtshan mo @171b rgyu dbang stong phrag bcu gnyis bshad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-1: 'gro la phan phyir 'jig rten bdag po bzhis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-2: 'bum phrag bzhi ni rab tu bshad pa yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-3: lha min dbang pos 'bum phrag gnyis nyid de //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-4: lha yi dbang pos kyang ni 'bum phrag gsum //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-5: gsang sngags phyag rgya sna tshogs cho gar ldan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-6: so so'i gzhung gi dkyil 'khor rnams dang bcas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-7: rang sngags rdo rje'i rjes 'brangs dad bskyed na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-8: ma bsgrims bzhin du the tshom med par 'grub //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-9: de las bzlog na dngos grub mi thob la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-10: sdug bsngal mang po yang ni 'thob par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-11: 'phags pa dpung bzang gis zhus pa'i le'u bcu pa'o ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-12: bcud kyis len dang gter dang phug 'gro dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-13: nor bsgyur 'byung khungs sngags dang gser bsgyur rtsi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-14: rin thang med pa'i rin chen nor sbyin te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-15: brgyad po bstan pa yongs su bsgrags pa yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-16: sngags dang phug tu 'gro dang bcud kyis len //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-17: sdig pa spong bar byed pa mchog tu bstan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-18: rin chen dang ni gter dang 'byung khungs 'bring //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-19: gser bsgyur rtsi dang nor bsgyur tha ma 'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-20: mi ni sems stobs ldan zhing chos la brtson //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-21: dka' thub gyis phyug dang por bstan pa'i snod //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-22: rdul shas che ba la ni 'bring por gsungs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-23: tha ma la ni mun pa can gyis bsten //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:171b-24: gang zhig mchog tu bstan pa bsten 'dod pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-2: gal te nor la sred cing sdug bsngal gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-3: gdungs na 'bring po la ni bstan par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-4: lha yi bde ba dang ni 'byor pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-5: tshe dang stobs gzugs phun sum tshogs pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-6: thos mang mdangs bzang gcig tu yid gzhungs dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-7: dbang thang che kun dka' thub stobs kyi 'thob //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-8: chags dang rnam bral dge la dga' ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-9: rtag tu dkon mchog gsum la sems gzhol dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-10: sdig pa spangs shing bzlas brjod ldan pa yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-11: mi la lha rdzas dngos grub ring ba med //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-12: rdo rje mtshon me gnam lcags mthu 'dra ba'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-13: gsang sngags mi yi 'jig rten mchog sbyin mdzad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-14: 'jig rten 'di dang pha rol nyid na yang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-15: sdug bsngal sel cing sdig 'joms gzhan med do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-16: gang zhig dpag bsam ljon pa'i shing lta bu //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-17: la lar dngos grub la lar bsod nams dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-18: gzhan la gzugs stobs che dang bde ba dag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-19: yid mthun 'bras bu 'dod pa'i mi la stsol //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-20: gsang sngags sna tshogs gzugs su rnam sprul nas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-21: gang zhig sdug bsngal gang zhig 'jigs skrag pa'am //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-22: rgyal po chom rkun thog gis 'jigs skrag pa'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-23: 'gro ba'i tshogs chen mtha' dag skyob par mdzad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172a-24: gang zhig yul dang khyim la bsten kyang rung //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-0: @172b dka' thub ma nyams rtse gcig sems kyis ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-1: nyin zhag gcig tu cung zad sngags bzlas na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-2: de yi gsang sngags dus shig na ni 'grub //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-3: cho ga bzhin du dang por 'bum bzlas nas; ;de nas sngags pa bsgrub la 'jug par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-4: de nas dngos grub myur du thob 'gyur la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-5: gsang sngags cho gas yun ring nyon mi mongs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-6: lus la sa yis dril phyis byas nas su //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-7: chu chen rnyog pa med par zhugs nas kyang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-8: ci tsam 'dod pa'i bar du khrus byas te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-9: byung nas shar ram byang du kha bltas nas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-10: chu yis lag pa rkang pa bkrus nas su //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-11: pus mo phyi rol du ni bstan byas te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-12: bar du lag bzhag tsog tsog por 'dug nas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-13: sgra med dbu ba med pas nye reg bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-14: lan gsum bar du chu ni 'thungs nas kyang; ;mchu la lan gnyis yongs su phyi bar bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-15: so la chags pa lce yis reg pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-16: sbrid pa byung na kha yang bkru bar bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-17: rab byung skyes pa bud med gzhon nu dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-18: gzhon nu ma dang bram ze rgan mo rnams //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-19: de la nam yang sngags pas reg mi bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-20: sngags pas de dag rnams la mi bsam mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-21: brgya la de dag rnams kyis reg gyur tam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-22: sgrub pos de dag rnams la reg gyur na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-23: slar yang khrus dang 'thor 'thung byas nas su //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:172b-24: de nas phyir yang bzlas la 'jug par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-0: gtsang sbra la dad zlos dga' snying @173a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-2: rtag tu len pa las ni log pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-3: slong mo'i zas za lha yi las la brtson //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-4: de yi lus la gsang sngags 'jug par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-5: 'ga' yis bud med gos dang nor rnams dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-6: bzhon pa rgyan dang byug pa bza' btung dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-7: mal stan rnams ni mang nyung byin gyur na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-8: de la sgrub la gnas par mi blang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-9: sa phung bshang sgor lnga ste mtshan la gsum //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-10: g-yon la gsum ste lag pa gnyis la bdun //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-11: yang na sa dang chu yis ji srid du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-12: dri ma dri bral de srid bar du bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-13: sos ka nags me mched pa'i me lce yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-14: ma bsgrims bzhin du tshang tshing kun bsregs ltar //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-15: bzlas brjod me la tshul khrims rlung gis sbar //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-16: brtson 'grus chen po'i me lces sdig pa sreg /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-17: ji ltar gangs la nyi ma'i 'od zer gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-18: gdungs na gzi brjid mi bzod 'ju ba bzhin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-19: tshul khrims nyi ma'i 'od zer bzlas brjod kyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-20: gdungs na sdig pa'i gangs kyang zad par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-21: mun nag smag la mar me phyung pa yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-22: mun nag ma lus sel bar byed pa ltar //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-23: tshe rabs stong na gnas pa'i sdig pa'i mun //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-24: bzlas brjod mar mes myur du sel bar byed //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173a-25: ci ste sbyin sreg dang ni bzlas brjod kyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-0: gsang sngags bsgrubs kyang dngos @173b grub ma thob na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-1: 'jim pa las ni mchod rten 'bum gdab pa'am //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-2: yang na chu 'gram bye ma dag la gdab //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-3: des ni de yi sdig pa srid gzhan la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-4: byas pa gang yin de ni zad gyur na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-5: des ni gsang sngags mthu yis 'di nyid du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-6: mthong ba'i chos la bsod nams 'bras bu thob //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-7: sngags kyi rtsa ba dang po tshul khrims te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-8: de nas brtson 'grus dang ni bzod pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-9: rgyal ba la ni dad dang byang chub sems //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-10: gsang sngags dang ni le lo med pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-11: de ltar mi dbang yan lag bdun ldan pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-12: skyo ba med par skye dgu 'dul bar byed //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-13: de bzhin sngags pa'ang yan lag 'di bdun dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-14: ldan par gyur na sdig pa 'dul bar byed //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-15: dang po bzlas brjod phal cher byas nas su //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-16: de yi 'og tu 'dir ni sbyin sreg bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-17: sbyin sreg dag gis gsang sngags mchog myur stsol //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-18: yid du 'ong ba'i 'dod pa'ang sbyin par mdzad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-19: gang gis dpag tshad brgya yi pha rol nas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-20: gsang sngags mthu yis bud med bkug kyang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-21: bud med ma yin gnod sbyin bu mo ste //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-22: de gzugs cha byad kyis ni sngags pa bsten //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-23: 'dod pa'i don phyir bsgrubs pa gang yin te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-24: grub na'ang gnod sbyin bu mos sbyin par byed //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-25: de ni bud med de yi lus su yang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:173b-26: sprul nas mtshan mo 'dod pa bsten par byed //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-2: bsten pa'i mi ni nor ni zad 'gyur ltar //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-3: de bzhin gnod sbyin mo 'am bran mo dag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-4: gsang sngags mthus bkug bsten par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-5: gzhan gyis chung mar yid la bzhag nas su //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-6: gang zhig de la 'dod gdungs sten byed pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-7: mi shes yid kyis gzhan gyi chung ma la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-8: 'dod pa spyad pas sdig pa mang du thob //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-9: rgyal ba la dang gzhan la phan brtson pa'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-10: lha klu lha min gnod sbyin dri za dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-11: grub par bcas pa'i sngags bshad gang yin pa; ;de dag rgyal ba'i nyan thos rang sangs rgyas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-12: de bzhin gshegs dang byang chub sems dpa' yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-13: ma 'ongs sems can mgon skyabs med rnams la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-14: rab tu gzigs nas byin gyis brlab pa mdzad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-15: de dag 'bras bu rab dang 'bring dang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-16: tha mar dbye bas rnam pa gsum du bstan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-17: mkha' la 'gro dang dpal gyi phug tu 'jug /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-18: 'dod dgu'i gzugs can mi snang rnam pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-19: gnod sbyin mo yi khyo dang bcud kyis len //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-20: mig 'phrul sgyu ma mtshan mo rgyu ba ste //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-21: de dag mchog yin 'bring ni sa bdag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-22: grong dang nor dang dbye dang dgug pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-23: dgar dang bskrad pa dang ni gsad pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174a-24: klu yi gdon gyis zin pa gso ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-0: @174b gang yang 'di lta bu dang mthun pa'i las //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-1: de ni mkhas pas phran tshegs yin par bstan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-2: bye phrag tu ni klu dang gnod sbyin dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-3: byis pa gdon gyis zin dang gang dag tu //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-4: lus can rnams la ngo mtshar sna tshogs dag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-5: ston par byed par phra mo phran tshegs yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-6: bya ba dang khu tshur thal lcag skra drang dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-7: rna bar bzlas dang dbang dang bskrad pa pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-8: bsad dang bcing la sogs pas tshar gcad dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-9: bod dang rig pa'i gos dang sngags gos dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-10: rdog pas bsnun dang rnam par bskyod pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-11: mig tu dug song [?] ltar ni gzhug pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-12: khab kyis gzugs dang kha bcing skyug tu gzhug /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-13: phu zhes bud dang yan lag gzhig pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-14: brang gis 'gro ba dag dang dgug pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-15: phyir yang bcing dang mnan par bya ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-16: rmongs par byed dang dug zar gzhug pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-17: dug ni gzhan la spo bar bya ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-18: lcags kyur ldan pas drang bar bya ba 'am //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-19: lus la zhen pa'i dug ni bslang ba 'am //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-20: zos par bza' dang zos pa bcad pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-21: sa bcing ba dang pho nya btang ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-22: bskrad pa dang ni klu la bstan pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-051:174b-23: dung dang rdza rnga'i sgras ni bslang pa ste //
